  lines:
  - english: Halt!
    swedish: Halt!
  - english: Drop your weapons!
    swedish: Slapp vapnen!
  - english: Stop right there!
    swedish: Stanna dar du ar!
  - english: You shall not get away with this!
    swedish: Detta undkommer du ej med!
  - english: Now you have brought blood upon yourself!
    swedish: Nu har du bringat blod over dig sjalv!
  - english: We shall have peace!
    swedish: Frid skall bevaras!
